-- Obama's Health-Care Law Ruled Unconstitutional Over Insurance Requirement
-- B y   T o m   S c h o e n b e r g
-- 2010-12-13T16:58:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-13/obama-health-law-is-ruled-unconstitutional-by-judge-over-insurance-mandate.html
 The Obama administration’s health-
care overhaul is unconstitutional because it forces individuals
to buy insurance, a federal judge said, striking down the
linchpin of the president’s plan.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
